data.description: Welcome! A large beautiful driveway invites you to come on inside and see this cozy 3 bed 2 bath home that sits on 2.58 Acres! This home features new flooring, new exterior paint, brand new deck patio, dishwasher, ceiling fan(s), a barn, and fully fenced yard! Relax on the back patio and surround yourself with nature. Make this property a hobby farm, workshop or tear down & build your dream home, endless possibilities!! Schedule your private showing today!
